# Master Control Protocol — paths never read, sent to an LLM, or included in audit context.
# Gitignore-style patterns (gitwildmatch). See AGENTS.md / CLAUDE.md.
# Merged with optional .mcpignore at the root of the repo being audited.

# Secrets and credentials
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
*.secret
**/secrets/
**/credentials/
**/vault/

# Sensitive config (broad — tune per org)
**/*secret*
**/*credential*
**/*password*
**/*token*

# Large binary / vendor / generated (token waste)
**/node_modules/
**/vendor/
**/.terraform/
**/dist/
**/build/
